mplicated systems. By\nconsidering the associated entropy increases up to second order in small volume\nchanges we argue that the consequences are in practice negligible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2015 10:59:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-07"}
